---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-secondary-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
        About Me
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert prose-headings:text-secondary-900 dark:prose-headings:text-white prose-a:text-primary-600 dark:prose-a:text-primary-400">
        <p class="lead">
          I'm a software engineer by profession and a filmmaker by passion. I believe stories have the power to connect us, whether they unfold through lines of code or frames of a camera.
        </p>
        
        <h2>My Journey</h2>
        <p>
          I had the incredible opportunity to work on The Passenger, a short film that went on to win awards and touch hearts. That experience taught me something priceless: life itself is the greatest story we ever get to tell.
        </p>
        
        <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
        <p>
          This space is where technology meets creativity, where code meets storytelling. Here, you'll find:
        </p>
        
        <ul>
          <li>Filmmaking insights and behind-the-scenes stories</li>
          <li>Life reflections and personal experiences</li>
          <li>Technical articles and software engineering perspectives</li>
          <li>Creative projects and works</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
        <p>
          Whether you're a fellow creative, a techie with a love for cinema, or just someone looking for a little inspiration, I hope you find something here that speaks to you. Let's explore stories, life, and a little bit of magic together.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-8 flex space-x-4">
          <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300">Twitter</a>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300">LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>